'''第90屆奧斯卡金像獎'''（{{lang-en|90th Academy Awards}}）是[[美国电影艺术与科学学会|美国电影艺术与科学学会]]為表彰[[2017年电影列表|2017年度傑出電影]]所頒發的獎項，頒獎典禮訂於2018年3月4日在[[加利福尼亚州|加州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的[[杜比剧院|杜比剧院]]舉行，共计颁发了24个类别的[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（也称「学院奖」）。頒獎典禮由美國廣播公司轉播。<ref name="dates">{{cite news|last1=Hipes|first1=Patrick|title=Oscars Dates Set For 2018 And Beyond|url=https://deadline.com/2017/04/oscars-2018-airdate-abc-academy-awards-dates-1202061171/|accessdate=2017-04-05|work=Deadline|date=2017-04-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170405053317/http://deadline.com/2017/04/oscars-2018-airdate-abc-academy-awards-dates-1202061171/|archivedate=2017-04-05}}</ref>[[吉米·坎摩爾|吉米·坎摩爾]]繼上年[[第89屆奧斯卡金像獎|第89屆奧斯卡金像獎]]後再度接下主持棒<ref>{{cite news|last=Thompson|first=Anne|title=Jimmy Kimmel Returning to Host the 2018 Oscars|url=http://collider.com/jimmy-kimmel-oscars-host-2018/#michael-de-luca|accessdate=2017-05-17|work=Collider|publisher=Complex|date=2017-05-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517031641/http://collider.com/jimmy-kimmel-oscars-host-2018/#michael-de-luca|archivedate=2017-05-17}}</ref>，该届奥斯卡颁奖典礼是继1974年[[第46届奥斯卡金像奖|第46届奥斯卡金像奖]]颁奖典礼以来收视率最低的一届。

== 入圍及得獎名單 ==
提名名單於[[太平洋时间|太平洋时间]]2018年1月23日上午5點22分（[[UTC|UTC]]13点22分）。在加利福尼亞州貝弗利山[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]公布，由演員[[安迪·瑟克斯|安迪·瑟克斯]]和[[蒂芬妮·哈戴許|蒂芬妮·哈戴許]]公布提名<ref>{{cite web|first=Ernest |last=Macias |title=Tiffany Haddish, Andy Serkis to announce Oscar nominations|url=http://ew.com/awards/2018/01/22/oscar-nominations-announcement-tiffany-haddish-andy-serkis/ |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2018-01-22|accessdate=2018-01-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220104835/http://ew.com/awards/2018/01/22/oscar-nominations-announcement-tiffany-haddish-andy-serkis/ |archivedate=2018-01-22}}</ref>。《[[水底情深|水底情深]]》以13項提名領跑，《[[敦克爾克大行動|敦克爾克大行動]]》則以8項緊隨其後<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/23/movies/oscar-nominations.html|script-title=en:2018 Oscar Nominations: ‘The Shape of Water’ Leads With 13 Nominations|date=2018-01-23|work=New York Times|accessdate=2018-01-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180123121052/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/23/movies/oscar-nominations.html|archivedate=2018-01-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/jan/23/oscars-2018-shape-of-water-leads-the-way-with-bumper-13-nominations|title=Oscars 2018: Shape of Water leads the way with bumper 13 nominations|date=2018-01-23|work=Guardian|accessdate=2018-01-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180123151920/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/jan/23/oscars-2018-shape-of-water-leads-the-way-with-bumper-13-nominations|archivedate=2018-01-23}}</ref>。

