== 典礼资讯 ==
[[File:JimmyKimmelHWOFJan2013.jpg|thumb]]為第90届奥斯卡金像奖的主持。]]
虽然[[第89届奥斯卡金像奖|去年颁奖典礼]]的口碑褒贬不一，学院还是连续第二年聘请{{tsl|en|Michael De Luca|麥克·迪·盧卡}}与{{tsl|en|Jennifer Todd|珍妮佛·陶德}}担任制片人<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr. |first1=Mike |title=Academy Setting Producers Mike De Luca & Jennifer Todd For 90th Oscars Encore |url=https://deadline.com/2017/03/oscar-producers-mike-de-luca-jennifer-todd-returning-90th-academy-awards-1202056062/ |accessdate=2017-03-30 |work=Deadline |date=2017-03-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103125108/https://deadline.com/2017/03/oscar-producers-mike-de-luca-jennifer-todd-returning-90th-academy-awards-1202056062/ |archivedate=2017-03-30}}</ref>。2017年5月，[[吉米·坎摩尔|吉米·坎摩尔]]据宣布将回归，连续第二年担任主持<ref>{{cite news|last1=Otterson |first1=Joe |title=Jimmy Kimmel Set to Host 2018 Oscars|url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/awards/jimmy-kimmel-2018-oscars-1202428589/|accessdate=2017-05-16|work=Variety |date=2017-05-16|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105032558/https://variety.com/2017/tv/awards/jimmy-kimmel-2018-oscars-1202428589/|archivedate=2017-05-16}}</ref>。再度被选为典礼司仪，坎摩尔表示他很震惊：“主持奥斯卡算是我职业生涯的一大亮点，很感谢谢丽尔（学院主席）和唐恩（执行制片），也谢谢学院让我回归，和我最喜欢的两个人迈克·迪·卢卡和珍妮佛·陶德共事。如果你觉得我们会搞砸今年的结尾，请坐等，直到你看到我们为90周年的节目计划了什么！<ref>{{cite web|title=Jimmy Kimmel Returns As Oscars 2018 Host|url=http://oscar.go.com/news/oscar-news/jimmy-kimmel-to-return-as-oscars-2018-host |publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |date=2017-09-06|accessdate=2017-12-06 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220095209/http://oscar.go.com/news/oscar-news/jimmy-kimmel-to-return-as-oscars-2018-host|archivedate=2017-12-20}}</ref>”吉米十分卖力地宣传典礼，拍摄了多则广告，还在他的脱口秀节目中讨论。

2017年2月4日，据宣布典礼和{{le|奥斯卡暖场秀|Academy Awards pre-show}}的时间将会变更，由于转播时间比之前提前了半个小时<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://oscar.go.com/news/oscar-news/new-broadcast-time-for-the-90th-oscars-announced|title=New broadcast time for the 90th Oscar announced|last=Dove|first=Steve|date=2017-12-04|website=Oscar|access-date=2017-12-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206141543/http://oscar.go.com/news/oscar-news/new-broadcast-time-for-the-90th-oscars-announced|archivedate=2017-12-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://popculture.com/2017/12/04/what-time-are-oscars-2018-movie-awards|title=Oscars Will Start 30 Minutes Earlier This Year|website=PopCulture.com|language=en|access-date=2017-12-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205143609/http://popculture.com/2017/12/04/what-time-are-oscars-2018-movie-awards/|archivedate=2017-12-05}}</ref>。本届提名揭晓仪式出现了[[佩麗冉卡·曹帕拉|佩麗冉卡·曹帕拉]]、[[罗莎里奥·道森|罗莎里奥·道森]]、[[盖尔·加朵|盖尔·加朵]]、[[莎瑪·希恩|莎瑪·希恩]]、[[米歇尔·罗德里格兹|米歇尔·罗德里格兹]]、[[佐伊·索尔达娜|佐伊·索尔达娜]]、{{le|莫莉·香侬|Molly Shannon}}、[[瑞贝尔·威尔森|瑞贝尔·威尔森]]和[[杨紫琼|杨紫琼]]分别献映的展现各奖项特色的小短片<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.oscars.org/news/90th-oscars-nominations-announcement|title=90th Oscars Nominations Announcement|date=2018-01-16|work=Academy of Motion Picture of Sciences|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180302214330/https://www.oscars.org/news/90th-oscars-nominations-announcement|archivedate=2018-03-02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/oscars-2018-nominations-live-stream-announcement-watch-2018-1|title=Watch the 2018 Oscar nominations announcement live right here|work=Business Insider|access-date=2018-01-23|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124070749/http://www.businessinsider.com/oscars-2018-nominations-live-stream-announcement-watch-2018-1|archivedate=2018-01-24}}</ref>。

依照往届传统，上一届的最佳男主角一般在下一届颁发最佳女主角奖，但去年的影帝[[卡西·阿弗莱克|卡西·阿弗莱克]]身陷性骚扰官司，他不打算出席典礼<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/sexual-misconduct/casey-affleck-skip-oscars-won-t-present-best-actress-award-n841251|title=Casey Affleck won't present best actress Oscar amid #MeToo spotlight|work=NBC News|access-date=2018-01-26|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126100920/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/sexual-misconduct/casey-affleck-skip-oscars-won-t-present-best-actress-award-n841251|archivedate=2018-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2018/01/casey-affleck-academy-awards-withdrawal-best-actress-me-too-movement-controversy-1202269196/|title=Casey Affleck Withdraws From Oscars: Won’t Present Best Actress Award|last=Jr|first=Mike Fleming|date=2018-01-25|work=Deadline|access-date=2018-01-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125223839/http://deadline.com/2018/01/casey-affleck-academy-awards-withdrawal-best-actress-me-too-movement-controversy-1202269196/|archivedate=2018-01-25}}</ref>。茱蒂·佛斯特和詹妮弗·劳伦斯顶替他发奖<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://variety.com/2018/film/in-contention/jennifer-lawrence-jodie-foster-oscars-casey-affleck-best-actress-1202715914/|title=Jennifer Lawrence and Jodie Foster to Present Best Actress Oscar, Replacing Casey Affleck (EXCLUSIVE)|last=Tapley|first=Kristopher|date=2018-03-02|work=Variety|access-date=2018-03-03|language=en-US|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303022829/http://variety.com/2018/film/in-contention/jennifer-lawrence-jodie-foster-oscars-casey-affleck-best-actress-1202715914/|archivedate=2018-03-03}}</ref>。最佳男演员奖由简·方达和海伦·米伦颁发<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ew.com/awards/2018/03/02/jennnifer-lawrence-jodie-foster-presenters-oscars/|title=Jennifer Lawrence, Jodie Foster reportedly presenting Best Actress at Oscars|work=EW.com|access-date=2018-03-03|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303195022/http://ew.com/awards/2018/03/02/jennnifer-lawrence-jodie-foster-presenters-oscars/|archivedate=2018-03-03}}</ref>。自[[第89届奥斯卡金像奖|颁错奖]]后，华伦·比提和费·唐娜薇今年再度颁发最佳影片奖<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://variety.com/2018/film/awards/oscars-faye-dunaway-warren-beatty-return-best-picture-1202715285/|title=Oscars: Faye Dunaway, Warren Beatty Expected to Return to Present Best Picture After Flub|last=Saperstein|first=Pat|date=2018-03-02|work=Variety|access-date=2018-03-03|language=en-US|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303024329/http://variety.com/2018/film/awards/oscars-faye-dunaway-warren-beatty-return-best-picture-1202715285/|archivedate=2018-03-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.goldderby.com/article/2018/2018-oscars-best-picture-presenters-warren-beatty-faye-dunaway-return-for-do-over/|title=2018 Oscars: Best Picture presenters Warren Beatty and Faye Dunaway return for do-over|last=Sheehan|first=Paul|date=2018-03-02|work=GoldDerby|access-date=2018-03-03|language=en-US|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303225600/http://www.goldderby.com/article/2018/2018-oscars-best-picture-presenters-warren-beatty-faye-dunaway-return-for-do-over/|archivedate=2018-03-03}}</ref>。

=== 影后奖杯被偷 ===
舞会后不久，影后弗朗西丝·麦克多曼德的奖杯被一名持有典礼后晚会门票的男子特瑞·布莱恩特（{{lang|en|Terry Bryant}}）偷走，15分钟奖杯被找回<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/03/05/movies/frances-mcdormand-stolen-oscar.html|title=Frances McDormand’s Oscar Is Stolen, Briefly, at the After-Party|last=Salam|first=Maya|date=2018-03-05|work=The New York Times|access-date=2018-03-08|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180308083513/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/03/05/movies/frances-mcdormand-stolen-oscar.html|archivedate=2018-03-08}}</ref>。布莱恩特自己拿着奖杯拍了短视频，还告诉其他客人自己是得奖者<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-43328696|title=Man denies stealing McDormand's Oscar|date=2018-03-08|work=BBC News|access-date=2018-03-08|language=en-GB|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180308150716/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-43328696|archivedate=2018-03-08}}</ref>。之后大厨{{le|沃尔夫冈·帕克|Wolfgang Puck}}的摄影师认得布莱恩特不是得奖者，当场将他拿下，将奖杯还给了影后<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2018/03/05/entertainment/frances-mcdormand-stolen-oscars/index.html|title=Frances McDormand's Oscar stolen (and returned)|last=CNN|first=Chloe Melas,|work=CNN|access-date=2018-03-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180307115926/https://edition.cnn.com/2018/03/05/entertainment/frances-mcdormand-stolen-oscars/index.html|archivedate=2018-03-07}}</ref> 。学院发表声明：“最佳女演员奖得主弗朗西丝·麦克多曼德在昨晚的舞会中和她的奥斯卡奖短暂分别后，高兴地重聚。据称小偷被一名摄影师、我们身手敏捷的学院会员及保安团队拿下<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/mar/05/frances-mcdormand-oscar-stolen-arrest|title=Man suspected of stealing Frances McDormand's Oscar arrested|last=Carroll|first=Rory|date=2018-03-05|website=the Guardian|language=en|access-date=2018-03-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180307124514/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/mar/05/frances-mcdormand-oscar-stolen-arrest|archivedate=2018-03-07}}</ref>。”尽管麦克多曼德同意放过布莱恩特，他还是被[[洛杉矶警察局|洛杉矶警察局]]逮捕，被控以[[偷窃|偷窃重罪]]。在星期三的听证会上，法官裁定“他没有弃保潜逃的风险”，判他无需缴纳保释释放，他将于2018年3月28日出庭<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/style/2018/03/frances-mcdormand-terry-bryant-oscars-statue-stolen-pleads-not-guilty|title=Frances McDormand’s Alleged Oscar Thief Admits He Took It, but Pleads Not Guilty|last=Bryant|first=Kenzie|work=Vanities|access-date=2018-03-08|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180309130907/https://www.vanityfair.com/style/2018/03/frances-mcdormand-terry-bryant-oscars-statue-stolen-pleads-not-guilty|archivedate=2018-03-09}}</ref>。

